title: PURINA Fancy Feast Dry Cat Food with Savory Chicken and Turkey - 7 lb. Bag (Pack of 2)
description: Like you, your feline demands the finer things in life, which is why she'll fall head over paws for this Purina Fancy Feast Gourmet Savory Chicken and Turkey dry cat food. Made in U.S. facilities, this kitty-approved gourmet dry cat food features a flavor collision that she can really wrap her taste buds around, with her favorite poultry tastes, chicken and turkey, rolled into one. Each bowlful provides your precocious princess with what she needs to keep her body healthy and strong, including 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition with the addition of vital minerals and nutrients. Each morsel of this gourmet food for cats comes lightly cooked and basted to give it a delicate crunch, ensuring her dish is always clean after meals. Your feline gets the goodness she craves while you get the satisfaction that you're feeding her the gold standard in nutritious food that leaves her licking her lips, hoping for more.
